    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for throughout its ownership. Mechanically, it is sound, with a smooth engine and transmission that make it a pleasure to drive. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing only light wear consistent with its age. On the exterior, the paint still holds a nice gloss, though you will find some minor stone chips and light surface scratches upon close inspection. It is a reliable, solid car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
